	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Hello, now I'm curious about this: How do I make manuals for NES games?<br /><br />Is there a template? Do I have to photoshop a random scan? Is there a certain size I should use?<br /><br />Any answer for any of these questions are fine. Thank You.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
